	<div class="summaryHolder">
		<div class="summary clearFix has-text-wrap">
			<p>Provides information about a specific culture (called a <em>locale</em> for unmanaged code development). The information includes the names for the culture, the writing system, the calendar used, the sort order of strings, and formatting for dates and numbers.</p>

		</div>
	</div>

